title: Justin Bieber shares video of Robbie Keane and Ireland celebrating their win ... - Salisbury Journal
text:
We know this because Keane sent the Biebs a video of Ireland celebrating on the team bus after their win over Germany, listening to the Canadian singer's track What Do You Mean? Love to my brother Keano and the Irish squad on a big win today. Got this vid of them listening to #WhatDoYouMean after the win.
 Salisbury Journal.
